A. S. WIKSTROM, Inc., as owner of THE A. S. WIKSTROM, Libelant-Appellee, v. MORANIA OIL TANKER CORP., as chartered owner of THE BILL ENDTER and THE MORANIA 130, Claimant-Respondent-Appellant. No. 265, Docket 23515. United States Court of Appeals Second Circuit. Argued April 11, 1955. Decided April 28, 1955. Leslie A. Hynes, New York City (Ne-vius, Brett & Kellogg, New York City, and Bond, Schoeneck & King, Syracuse, N. Y., on the brief), for libelant-appel-lee. John A. Lyon, New York City (Pla-tow & Lyon, New York City, on the brief), for claimant-respondent-appellant.

Before CLARK, Chief Judge, and FRANK and HASTIE, Circuit Judges.

PER CURIAM.

Affirmed on the opinion of District Judge Brennan, 131 F.Supp. 240.
